ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Amending the Canadian Passport Order
PrecisOrder Amending the CANADIAN PASSPORT ORDER in order to clarify issues around revocation and cancellation of passports and provide express authorities for the Minister of Immigration, Refugees and Citizenship to introduce automated processing and decision making to the Passport Program.
